596
00:33:00,201 --> 00:33:00,921
to pass to me?

597
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:03,681
The bush roses in the yard

598
00:33:04,721 --> 00:33:05,881
bloomed beautifully

599
00:33:06,800 --> 00:33:07,481
