624
00:34:21,017 --> 00:34:22,561
♪After braving storms♪

625
00:34:22,855 --> 00:34:26,812
♪There is also a harbor of refuge♪

626
00:34:27,051 --> 00:34:29,734
♪Stumbling all the way through♪

627
00:34:29,955 --> 00:34:32,933
♪Starting and stopping,
coming and going♪

628
00:34:36,651 --> 00:34:40,260
