632
00:34:50,793 --> 00:34:54,327
"♪What does the wear
and tear of time mean♪"

633
00:34:54,421 --> 00:34:58,095
♪Both tears and laughter will shine♪

634
00:34:58,275 --> 00:35:00,885
♪Even in a sigh♪

635
00:35:01,012 --> 00:35:06,326
♪The heart knows it's worth it♪

636
00:35:09,406 --> 00:35:12,657
♪I'm lucky to have you by my side♪

637
00:35:13,032 --> 00:35:20,488
♪Everything that's happening
is the best♪

638
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:21,480
Alright, Ms. Wang.

639
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:22,201
Ms. Wang,

640
00:35:22,201 --> 00:35:22,960
that's enough.

641
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,001
So sorry,

642
00:35:25,001 --> 00:35:26,121
it's quite late now.

643
00:35:27,201 --> 00:35:28,641
We have a special situation tonight.

644
00:35:30,041 --> 00:35:30,561
Sure, young lad.

645
00:35:30,681 --> 00:35:31,280
I have already

646
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,161
talked to Mr. Liu.

647
00:35:32,241 --> 00:35:32,840
For tonight's work,

648
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,201
we will

649
00:35:34,360 --> 00:35:34,960
double the wage.

650
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,320
Thank you, Mr. Chai.

651
00:35:36,400 --> 00:35:36,840
Thanks for your hard work.

652
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:37,360
Sorry to trouble you.

653
00:35:37,561 --> 00:35:37,960
Thanks.

654
00:35:38,241 --> 00:35:38,721
Thanks.

655
00:35:39,041 --> 00:35:39,480
Alright.

656
00:35:40,001 --> 00:35:40,521
Take care.

657
00:35:45,081 --> 00:35:46,201
It's all cleaned up.

658
00:35:47,041 --> 00:35:48,001
Thanks, Boss Chai.

659
00:35:48,800 --> 00:35:49,521
What for?

660
00:35:49,681 --> 00:35:50,561
Are Mum and Dad asleep?

661
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:51,561
Yes.

662
00:35:51,800 --> 00:35:52,201
Good.

663
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:52,960
It's getting late,

664
00:35:52,960 --> 00:35:53,800
you should also go to bed.

665
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:54,840
I'll leave now.

666
00:35:54,960 --> 00:35:55,760
You guys should go,

667
00:35:55,800 --> 00:35:56,400
I'm right here.

668
00:35:58,041 --> 00:35:58,721
I'll send you home.

669
00:35:59,280 --> 00:35:59,840
Sure.

670
