676
00:36:16,001 --> 00:36:16,880
Isn't this what I should do?

677
00:36:17,601 --> 00:36:18,601
Take care of Mum and Dad.

678
00:36:22,161 --> 00:36:23,041
Have a good rest.

679
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:36,960
Boss,

680
00:36:38,601 --> 00:36:39,480
