681
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,400
You are always so polite.

682
00:36:45,081 --> 00:36:46,241
Is this fun to you?

683
00:36:51,440 --> 00:36:52,601
It seems that human

684
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:55,201
really does evolve.

685
00:36:57,960 --> 00:36:58,681
Thinking back,

686
00:36:59,521 --> 00:37:00,880
when I first met you,

687
00:37:02,201 --> 00:37:03,721
