694
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,960
Is it because you tied your hair

695
00:37:17,360 --> 00:37:18,320
too tightly back then

696
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,721
and caused receding hairline?

697
00:37:20,521 --> 00:37:21,280
That's nonsense.

698
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:26,521
That's right.

699
00:37:27,320 --> 00:37:28,360
Aren't we back?

700
00:37:30,161 --> 00:37:31,641
At that time, as soon as
you entered the door

701
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,480
and found out that I was
the interviewer,

702
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:36,320
not only was you not afraid,

703
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,001
you even smiled at me,

704
00:37:38,641 --> 00:37:39,320
exposing a total of

705
00:37:40,001 --> 00:37:41,241
eight big white teeth.

706
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:43,001
What a sycophantic smile.

707
00:37:43,480 --> 00:37:45,121
It was a bright smile.

708
00:37:46,641 --> 00:37:47,521
Later we chatted

709
00:37:49,480 --> 00:37:50,280
and found out that we actually

710
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:51,760
studied in the same school.

711
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:54,561
You said this was fate,

712
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,121
and I was thinking

713
00:37:58,121 --> 00:37:58,920
that surprisingly,

714
00:37:59,320 --> 00:38:00,800
our school actually cultivated

715
00:38:00,920 --> 00:38:02,201
such a thick-skinned person

716
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:04,241
who is perfect for sales.

717
00:38:05,201 --> 00:38:06,241
You must think you have

718
00:38:06,280 --> 00:38:07,440
pretty good eye
for things now, don't you?

719
00:38:14,601 --> 00:38:15,800
In my impression,

720
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:18,201
you are still that young woman
in her twenties,

721
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,161
a fresh flower.

722
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:20,920
In the blink of an eye,

723
00:38:22,880 --> 00:38:23,641
it's almost time

724
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:24,641
for your babies to go to school.

725
00:38:27,161 --> 00:38:28,561
They both need to grow slower.

726
00:38:30,201 --> 00:38:31,480
When they are both grown up,

727
00:38:31,521 --> 00:38:33,121
I... I will be old then.

728
00:38:34,360 --> 00:38:35,641
That's one thing,

729
00:38:37,081 --> 00:38:38,641
but we won't be withered yet.

