776
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:03,880
I'll eat whatever you make.

777
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,201
Let's just take some small bites.

778
00:42:07,280 --> 00:42:07,800
Sure.

779
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:09,400
Go get some more sleep.

780
00:42:09,561 --> 00:42:10,561
I'll wake you up when breakfast's ready.

781
00:42:11,521 --> 00:42:12,041
Sure.

